            </p>

            <h3 class="policy-h3 mt-8">Right to Lodge a Complaint</h3>
            <p>
              You have the right to lodge a complaint with your local supervisory authority.
              For EU residents, find your national DPA at
              <a href="https://edpb.europa.eu/about-edpb/about-edpb/members_en" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">edpb.europa.eu</a>.
              For UK residents, contact the
              <a href="https://ico.org.uk/make-a-complaint/" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Information Commissioner's Office (ICO)</a>.
            </p>

            <h3 class="policy-h3 mt-8">Automated Decision-Making</h3>
            <p>
              SlayCal generates personalised calorie goals and nutrition targets based on your
